  "narrative": "# Turn 63\n\n*7 commanders issued orders this turn.*\n\n## Strategic Decisions\n\n### CURATOR (artifact collector)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W22, W27.\n\n### NOMAD (merchant)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W8, W32.\n\nEconomic activity: commissioned 18 new ships.\n\n### PROPHET (apostle)\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 1 fleets; unloaded at 2 destinations; commissioned 10 new ships.\n\n### REAVER (pirate)\n\nDispatched 4 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W12, W31, W17, W7.\n\n### SOLARIS (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W19, W20.\n\n### TERRAN (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W14, W24.\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 1 fleets; unloaded at 1 destinations; commissioned 28 new ships; invested in 2 units of industry.\n\n### TRADER (merchant)\n\nDispatched 3 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W30, W30, W14.\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 1 fleets; commissioned 6 new ships.\n\n## Consequences\n\n### Territorial Shifts\n\n- **REAVER** seized control of W17 (previously TRADER).\n\n- **SOLARIS** seized control of W19 (previously TERRAN).\n\n- **TRADER** seized control of W30 (previously NOMAD).\n\n- **NOMAD** seized control of W32 (previously TRADER).\n\n### Fleet Movements\n\n- **CURATOR** moved: F7\u2192W22, F8\u2192W27\n\n- **NOMAD** moved: F16\u2192W8, F15\u2192W32\n\n- **REAVER** repositioned 4 fleets across the sector.\n\n- **SOLARIS** moved: F1\u2192W19, F2\u2192W20\n\n- **TERRAN** moved: F14\u2192W14, F13\u2192W24\n\n- **TRADER** moved: F4\u2192W30, F3\u2192W14\n\n### Production\n\n- **NOMAD** launched 18 new ships.\n\n- **PROPHET** launched 10 new ships.\n\n- **TERRAN** launched 5 new ships.\n\n- **TRADER** launched 0 new ships.\n\n- **TERRAN** built 2 industry.\n\n### Diplomacy\n\n- **TRADER** sent a message to **NOMAD**: *\"Alliance Proposal from TRADER\"*\n"
